text: Svetlana Bortnikova (; born 17 June 1997) is a Kazakhstani footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Kazakhstan women's national team. ==Career== Bortnikova has been capped for the Kazakhstan national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani women's footballers Category:Kazakhstan women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:BIIK Kazygurt players
